Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢过的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳憬过的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满怀思念的尽头所看到的东西是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恨还是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  死后文
